OL,3,CFamily's criticism after father's
OL,4,Ckiller moved to open prison
OL,6,FRelatives of a man who was murdered by
OL,7,Fhis partner say they are furious after
OL,8,Flearning she will be moved to an open
OL,9,Fprison.
OL,11,FBarry O'Brien, 41, was stabbed to
OL,12,Fdeath by Lisa Glover in 2014 at the
OL,13,Fhouse they shared in Scunthorpe,
OL,14,FLincolnshire.
OL,16,FGlover was later jailed for life with
OL,17,Fa minimum 14-year term at Hull Crown
OL,18,FCourt after a judge described Mr
OL,19,FO'Brien's death as "premature and
OL,20,Fviolent".
