OL,3,CFamily's criticism after father's
OL,4,Ckiller moved to open prison
OL,6,FBut Glover was this year moved to an
OL,7,Fopen prison 11 years into her sentence
OL,8,Fin a decision criticised by Mr
OL,9,FO'Brien's family as a "betrayal" by
OL,10,Fthe justice system.
OL,12,FIt is understood she is now in custody
OL,13,Fat HMP Askham Grange, near York.
OL,15,FMr O'Brien's daughter Caitlin was 14
OL,16,Fwhen she lost her father. She said the
OL,17,Fnews showed the impact statement she
OL,18,Fgave to the court at the time had been
OL,19,Fignored.
