OL,3,CFamily's criticism after father's
OL,4,Ckiller moved to open prison
OL,6,F"Having all that pain, that hurt, that
OL,7,Fgrief brought up again, to not even be
OL,8,Flistened to (and) my statement not
OL,9,Feven taken into account, just made me
OL,10,Ffeel like I don't have a voice and my
OL,11,Ffeelings don't matter.
OL,13,F"It's just something I'll never come
OL,14,Fto terms with.
OL,16,F"She took my dad's freedom away - why
OL,17,Fshould she get her life back when my
OL,18,Fdad's never going to get that?
