OL,6,FShe claims she also learned Glover had
OL,7,Fbeen allowed to have a family
OL,8,Fphotoshoot in prison 10 months into
OL,9,Fher sentence.
OL,11,FOpen prisons allow inmates some
OL,12,Fdegrees of freedom under restricted
OL,13,Fconditions, and are often used to
OL,14,Frehabilitate or prepare offenders for
OL,15,Freturning to society.
OL,17,FNicola Heseltine, Mr O'Brien's former
OL,18,Fpartner and Caitlin's mother, said:
OL,19,F"We just feel completely let down by
OL,20,Fthe service.
