OL,6,F"We're not here for revenge or
OL,7,Fanything like that, we're just here
OL,8,Ffor their voices to be heard, and how
OL,9,Fvictims should have their say, and how
OL,10,Fit does impact them. Just because
OL,11,Fprisons are full, doesn't mean she
OL,12,Fshould be able to move on with her
OL,13,Flife. "
OL,15,FIn a response to concerns raised by
OL,16,Fthe family's MP Nic Dakin, victims
OL,17,Fminister Alex Davies-Jones said their
OL,18,Fstatement had been "taken into
OL,19,Fconsideration" and that the family
OL,20,Fwere "kept informed", although Nicola
OL,21,Fsays this is not true.
