OL,10,FChancellorto approve decisions without
OL,11,FParole Board hearings.
OL,13,FA Ministry of Justice spokesperson
OL,14,Fsaid: "This was a horrific crime and
OL,15,Four thoughts remain with the victim's
OL,16,Ffamily.
